-- Shell Says Will ‘Challenge’ Nigeria’s $5 Billion Oil Spill Fine
-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 2012-07-18T14:59:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-18/shell-says-will-challenge-nigeria-s-5-billion-oil-spill-fine.html
Royal Dutch Shell Plc (RDSA) ’s Nigerian
unit said it will fight a $5 billlion fine for spill at the
company’s offshore Bonga field.  “Shell Nigeria Exploration and Production Co. will
challenge any attempt to impose such a penalty,” Managing
Director Chike Onyejekwe said today in an emailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
